title: Kansas fans celebrate win over Duke as team heads to Final Four
text:
Kansas fans celebrate win over Duke as team heads to Final Four Monday, March 26, 2018 - 00:39 
University of Kansas' basketball team is heading to the Final Four after beating Duke University 85-81 Sunday night at CenturyLink Center in Omaha, Nebraska. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
